HOW TO USE

 ● Push the TRANSMIT button on the watch;

 ● Mount the watch approximately in the place where the speaker is located;

 ● Push the M-A M-B buttons to make sure that the connection is established;

 ● If necessary, moving the watch, find a place with a better connection;

 ● For some phones, you can try setting the option "Antiphase" to improve communication;

 ● To reset the watch, long press "RST", then hold down all 4 buttons on the watch and wait a couple of seconds.
